description:
PSPDFKit for Windows
    
    PSPDFKit for Windows is being sunset, in line with Microsoft’s decision to gradually phase out UWP by limiting updates to bug fixes and security patches. All UWP licenses will continue to work and be supported until 1 December 2026, or until your license expires, whichever occurs later. Interested in transitioning to another Nutrient product? Contact us and we’ll be happy to help.
title: PSPDFKit for UWP
